name: NEW! Girl On Fire Necklace

What is gold filled?

Gold Filled is not like gold plated as there is approx 100 times more gold in gold fill, than there is on plated. Gold filled looks and usually wears as well as karat gold. Often referred to as rolled gold, gold fill is very hard wearing and should last under normal wear conditions for a lifetime.
